IBADAN – The People’s Democratic Party House of Representatives Candidate, in Ibadan North Federal Constituency, Hon. ‘Lanre Sarumi, has extended warm felicitations to Oyo State Party’s Secretary, Hon. Wasiu Adeleke on the occasion of his birthday, describing him as a goal-getter. The House of Representatives hopeful, in a statement made available to newsmen today in Ibadan wished Adeleke more glorious years of outstanding service to the State and tremendous successes in the party. Joining well-wishers in rejoicing with Hon. Adeleke, Sarumi described him as an outstanding leader. He further described Hon. Adeleke as a man of impeccable character, who has propelled the activities of the party in the state to enviable heights. According to him, “You are one the most vibrant and capable scribe our great party has produced. You role in grasssroots mobilisation has sold the party to both affluent and the downtrodden in our society.” “I, on behalf of my family, friends and political associates, congratulate you on your birthday. May the years ahead offer you great moments of accomplishment and desired victories, even as you continue to stand firm in service to God and mankind,” he added.